		<h1 class="entry-title">Career Opportunities</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p style="text-align: left;">Charter Software Inc. is a medium-sized and growing software company founded in 1978 and located in Littleton, Colorado.</p>
<div class="category-desc">
<div>Our flagship product, a Windows-based business management system, was designed exclusively for equipment dealerships. We are the only business system vendor endorsed by five regional equipment dealer associations in the United States and Canada.</div>
<div></div>
<div>We enjoy working in a casual, but professional environment and offer an excellent benefits package including vacation, holiday, Simple IRA, health, medical, and dental.</div>
<div></div>
<div></div>
<div><strong>Following are our current full-time openings:</strong></div>
